cluster-glue: cluster-glue (Reusable Cluster Components)
cluster-glue: 
cluster-glue: Additional cluster tools to play with e.g. some STONITH scripts.
cluster-glue: 
cluster-glue: You might also want to install corosync, pacemaker, resource-agents,
cluster-glue: crmsh, fence-agents and eventually cluster-glue.
cluster-glue: 
cluster-glue: You must have a haclient group and hacluster user to run this script.
cluster-glue:   groupadd -g 226 haclient
cluster-glue:   useradd -u 226 -g 226 -c "Pacemaker" -d / -s /bin/false hacluster
